at all times. Again, lots of resources here. I definitely recommend R ladies and R users

00:03:51.020 --> 00:03:54.500
groups to learn these in person, because then you can ask questions and things like that.

00:03:54.500 --> 00:03:58.220
Try to learn new things, try to keep on top of trends, and it could make your life a lot

